WEBVTT

00:00.023 --> 00:03.579
Children's Day is celebrated in many countries on different days...

00:03.686 --> 00:05.051
...and in their own unique style.

00:05.255 --> 00:09.771
Parents spend time with their kids by taking them to the zoo, museum, amusement park,...

00:10.011 --> 00:12.262
...movie theater and other fun places.

00:12.471 --> 00:14.402
In addition, children receive gifts.

00:14.499 --> 00:16.909
Special events take place throughout the country,...

00:17.102 --> 00:21.358
...from parades to festivals, to athletic competitions and craft fairs.

00:21.453 --> 00:22.579
It's all for the children,...

00:22.737 --> 00:26.084
...and not to mention, children get to enjoy their favorite yummy foods.

